topic.title: Found Bug on Channel Oage List (Solution Included)
topic.body:
There's a div that is covering the list of channels on this site. The div has a class of "channels-sidebar col-lg-3". When the class is removed, the individual channels appear. I used the tor bundle.

http://127.0.0.1:43110/1J1c7eML6uMwDU4uiKbKRxoqxGP6WMFMvb/index.html?view:channels
